xwikidoc.content: <bvancea> has joined #medsavant 07:34 <mcupak> has joined #medsavant 11:39 <sdumitriu1> has joined #medsavant 12:17 <bvancea> sdumitriu, can I un-install savant on windows? 12:22 <sdumitriu1> has joined #medsavant 16:51 <sdumitriu> bvancea: You can if you use the jar installer 17:14 <bvancea> I see, thanks 17:14 <sdumitriu> bvancea: Re-install, then uninstall should work 17:15 <bvancea> it did 17:17 <bvancea> I un-installed and reinstalled again, it works nicely with the jar installer 17:17 <bvancea> cannot reproduce the original exception thrown by the client though 17:25 <bvancea> well, I'm off to bed, good night
